<!doctype html>
<html>
<head><%- include('partials/head', { title: 'API Keys' }) %></head>
<body class="bg-slate-100 min-h-screen">
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-6 space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">API Keys</h1>
    <% if (flash) { %><div class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm"><%= flash %></div><% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/apikeys" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex gap-2 text-sm">
      <input name="label" placeholder="Label, mis. bot-telegram-prod" class="border rounded px-3 py-2 flex-1" required />
      <button class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">Buat API Key</button>
    </form>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-500">
          <tr>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2">Label</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2">Public Key</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2">Secret</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2">Status</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2"></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% keys.forEach(function(k) { %>
            <tr class="border-t">
              <td class="px-4 py-2"><%= k.label %></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs"><%= k.key %></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-slate-500"><%= k.secret.slice(0, 6) %>…<%= k.secret.slice(-4) %></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs <%= k.isActive ? 'bg-green-100 text-green-700' : 'bg-slate-200 text-slate-600' %>"><%= k.isActive ? 'AKTIF' : 'NONAKTIF' %></span></td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2 space-x-2">
                <form method="POST" action="/apikeys/<%= k.id %>/toggle" class="inline"><button class="text-xs text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900">Toggle</button></form>
                <form method="POST" action="/apikeys/<%= k.id %>/delete" class="inline" onsubmit="return confirm('Hapus API key ini?')"><button class="text-xs text-red-600 hover:text-red-800">Hapus</button></form>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% }) %>
          <% if (!keys.length) { %>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-6 text-center text-slate-400" colspan="5">Belum ada API key.</td></tr>
          <% } %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- =================================================================== -->
    <!-- API DOCUMENTATION                                                    -->
    <!-- =================================================================== -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6 space-y-6" id="docs">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">📖 API Documentation</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Semua yang perlu untuk integrasi ke bot Telegram / aplikasi kamu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs bg-slate-100 rounded px-3 py-2 font-mono">
          Base URL:<br />
          <span class="text-slate-800" id="baseUrlDisplay"><%= baseUrl %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ Auth ============ -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">1. Authentication</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">
          Setiap request ke <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1 rounded">/api/v1/*</code> wajib
          menyertakan header <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1 rounded">X-API-Key</code>
          berisi <em>public key</em>-mu (yang diawali <code>pk_</code>).
        </p>
        <pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs mt-2 overflow-x-auto"><code>X-API-Key: pk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</code></pre>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">
          <em>Secret key</em> (yang diawali <code>sk_</code>) TIDAK digunakan di request —
          dia dipakai server untuk sign webhook (HMAC-SHA256) sehingga bot kamu
          bisa verify webhook itu asli dari PG ini.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ Endpoints ============ -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">2. Endpoints</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-sm">

          <!-- Create invoice -->
          <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-emerald-600 text-white px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
              <span class="bg-emerald-800 rounded px-2 py-0.5">POST</span>
              <span>/api/v1/invoices</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-emerald-100">Buat invoice baru</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 space-y-2">
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Request body (JSON)</div>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>{
  "amount": 1000,                          // WAJIB. Integer rupiah, tanpa unique code.
  "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42",              // OPSIONAL. ID transaksi di sistemmu.
  "description": "Beli topup 1rb",         // OPSIONAL.
  "callback_url": "https://mybot/hook",    // OPSIONAL. Webhook saat invoice PAID.
  "provider_id": 1                         // OPSIONAL. Default: provider aktif pertama.
}</code></pre>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Response 200 OK</div>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>{
  "reference":         "INV-XXXXXXXXXX",     // ID public. Simpan ini!
  "merchant_ref":      "ORDER-42",
  "amount":            1000,                 // Nominal asli
  "unique_code":       342,                  // 1-999, ditambahkan biar unique
  "total_amount":      1342,                 // Nominal YANG HARUS DIBAYAR
  "status":            "PENDING",
  "qris_string":       "00020101021226...",  // Bisa di-render sendiri jadi QR
  "qris_image":        "data:image/png;base64,...", // PNG siap pakai
  "expired_at":        "2026-07-23T05:00:00.000Z",
  "pay_url":           "<%= baseUrl %>/pay/INV-XXXXXXXXXX",
  "idempotent_replay": false                 // true = invoice existing dikembalikan
}</code></pre>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded p-2 text-xs text-amber-900">
                <div class="font-semibold mb-1">🔁 Idempotency via <code>merchant_ref</code></div>
                Kalau kamu retry POST dengan <code>merchant_ref</code> yang SAMA
                (mis. karena bot Telegram-mu timeout &amp; retry), request kedua
                <strong>tidak</strong> bikin invoice baru — kita balikin invoice
                PENDING yang sama. Header response berisi
                <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">X-Idempotent-Replay: true</code>
                dan field <code>idempotent_replay: true</code>. Aman untuk
                di-retry tanpa risiko duplikat.
                <div class="mt-1">
                  Kalau <code>merchant_ref</code> sama tapi <code>amount</code> beda →
                  ditolak dengan HTTP 409 (<code>merchant_ref_conflict</code>).
                  Cancel invoice lama dulu, atau pakai <code>merchant_ref</code> lain.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">
                💡 Bot Telegram tinggal ambil <code>qris_image</code> (data URL base64),
                decode ke bytes, terus kirim pakai <code>sendPhoto</code>. Atau kirim
                <code>pay_url</code> supaya user buka di browser &amp; scan QR di halaman itu.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Get invoice -->
          <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-sky-600 text-white px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
              <span class="bg-sky-800 rounded px-2 py-0.5">GET</span>
              <span>/api/v1/invoices/:reference</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-sky-100">Cek status invoice</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 space-y-2">
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-1">Response 200 OK</div>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>{
  "reference":    "INV-XXXXXXXXXX",
  "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42",
  "amount":       1000,
  "unique_code":  342,
  "total_amount": 1342,
  "status":       "PAID",                    // PENDING | PAID | EXPIRED | CANCELLED
  "paid_at":      "2026-07-23T04:05:12.000Z",
  "expired_at":   "2026-07-23T05:00:00.000Z",
  "pay_url":      "<%= baseUrl %>/pay/INV-XXXXXXXXXX"
}</code></pre>
              </div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">
                Bot bisa poll endpoint ini tiap 3-5 detik sampai status berubah ke
                <code>PAID</code> / <code>EXPIRED</code> / <code>CANCELLED</code>.
                Alternatif lebih hemat: pakai webhook <code>callback_url</code>.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cancel invoice -->
          <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-rose-600 text-white px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono">
              <span class="bg-rose-800 rounded px-2 py-0.5">POST</span>
              <span>/api/v1/invoices/:reference/cancel</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-rose-100">Batalkan invoice PENDING</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 space-y-2">
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>{ "ok": true }</code></pre>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Cuma bisa cancel invoice yang statusnya masih <code>PENDING</code>.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ Webhook ============ -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">3. Webhook (opsional tapi direkomendasikan)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">
          Kalau kamu isi <code>callback_url</code> waktu bikin invoice, PG akan
          POST payload berikut ke URL itu <strong>begitu invoice jadi PAID</strong>.
          Retry 3× dengan jeda 2 detik kalau responsemu non-2xx.
        </p>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs mt-2 overflow-x-auto"><code>Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Event:      invoice.paid
  X-Signature:  HMAC-SHA256(rawBody, apiKey.secret)   // hex-encoded

Body:
{
  "event":        "invoice.paid",
  "reference":    "INV-XXXXXXXXXX",
  "merchantRef":  "ORDER-42",
  "amount":       1000,
  "uniqueCode":   342,
  "totalAmount":  1342,
  "status":       "PAID",
  "paidAt":       "2026-07-23T04:05:12.000Z",
  "providerType": "orderkuota_jywa"
}</code></pre>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">
          Verify di sisi bot (Python):
        </p>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs mt-1 overflow-x-auto"><code>import hmac, hashlib
expected = hmac.new(SECRET.encode(), raw_body, hashlib.sha256).hexdigest()
if expected != request.headers.get("X-Signature"):
    return 401</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ Error codes ============ -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">4. Error responses</h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">
          <table class="w-full text-xs mt-2">
            <thead class="text-slate-500">
              <tr class="border-b">
                <th class="text-left py-1 pr-3">HTTP</th>
                <th class="text-left py-1 pr-3">error code</th>
                <th class="text-left py-1">Kenapa &amp; cara handle di bot</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="font-mono">
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">401</td><td class="pr-3">missing_api_key / invalid_api_key</td><td class="font-sans">Header X-API-Key salah / kosong / nonaktif.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">400</td><td class="pr-3">invalid_amount</td><td class="font-sans">Amount bukan integer positif atau &gt; 9.999.000.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">400</td><td class="pr-3">provider_not_found / provider_inactive</td><td class="font-sans"><code>provider_id</code> tidak ada / non-aktif.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">400</td><td class="pr-3">no_active_provider</td><td class="font-sans">Belum ada Provider aktif di dashboard.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">400</td><td class="pr-3">bad_request</td><td class="font-sans">Body JSON invalid / field wajib kosong.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b bg-amber-50"><td class="py-1 pr-3">409</td><td class="pr-3">merchant_ref_conflict</td><td class="font-sans"><code>merchant_ref</code> sudah dipakai invoice PENDING lain dengan amount berbeda. Cancel dulu / pakai ref lain.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b bg-amber-50"><td class="py-1 pr-3">429</td><td class="pr-3">unique_code_pool_exhausted</td><td class="font-sans">&gt; 999 invoice PENDING dgn amount sama. Response menyertakan header <code>Retry-After: 10</code>. <strong>Bot: sleep 10 detik lalu retry</strong>, atau varietasikan amount.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">404</td><td class="pr-3">not_found</td><td class="font-sans">Reference invoice tidak ditemukan.</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="py-1 pr-3">403</td><td class="pr-3">forbidden</td><td class="font-sans">API key ini bukan pemilik invoice tsb.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-1 pr-3">400</td><td class="pr-3">invalid_state</td><td class="font-sans">Cancel dipanggil ke invoice non-PENDING.</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ Code examples ============ -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800">5. Contoh Kode</h3>

        <!-- Language tabs -->
        <div class="mt-3 border-b flex gap-1 text-xs">
          <button data-tab="curl" class="tab-btn px-3 py-2 border-b-2 border-slate-900 font-semibold">cURL</button>
          <button data-tab="python" class="tab-btn px-3 py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900">Python (requests)</button>
          <button data-tab="pyTelegramBot" class="tab-btn px-3 py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900">🤖 Bot Telegram (Python)</button>
          <button data-tab="node" class="tab-btn px-3 py-2 border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900">Node.js (axios)</button>
        </div>

        <!-- cURL -->
        <div class="tab-panel" data-tab="curl">
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 mb-1">Buat invoice</div>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>curl -X POST <%= baseUrl %>/api/v1/invoices \
  -H "X-API-Key: pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"amount": 1000, "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42", "description": "Test"}'</code></pre>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 mb-1">Cek status</div>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>curl <%= baseUrl %>/api/v1/invoices/INV-XXXXXXXXXX \
  -H "X-API-Key: pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"</code></pre>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 mb-1">Cancel</div>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>curl -X POST <%= baseUrl %>/api/v1/invoices/INV-XXXXXXXXXX/cancel \
  -H "X-API-Key: pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"</code></pre>
        </div>

        <!-- Python -->
        <div class="tab-panel hidden" data-tab="python">
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs mt-3 overflow-x-auto"><code>import requests

BASE = "<%= baseUrl %>"
KEY  = "pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"
H    = {"X-API-Key": KEY, "Content-Type": "application/json"}

# 1. Buat invoice
r = requests.post(f"{BASE}/api/v1/invoices", headers=H, json={
    "amount":       1000,
    "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42",
    "description":  "Test dari Python",
})
r.raise_for_status()
inv = r.json()
print("Reference:", inv["reference"])
print("Bayar Rp", inv["total_amount"])
print("Pay URL :", inv["pay_url"])

# 2. Simpan QRIS jadi file PNG
import base64
png_b64 = inv["qris_image"].split(",", 1)[1]
with open("qris.png", "wb") as f:
    f.write(base64.b64decode(png_b64))

# 3. Poll status tiap 3 detik sampai PAID atau EXPIRED
import time
while True:
    s = requests.get(f"{BASE}/api/v1/invoices/{inv['reference']}", headers=H).json()
    print("Status:", s["status"])
    if s["status"] in ("PAID", "EXPIRED", "CANCELLED"):
        break
    time.sleep(3)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <!-- Python Telegram Bot -->
        <div class="tab-panel hidden" data-tab="pyTelegramBot">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3">Contoh minimal pakai
            <a class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/python-telegram-bot/python-telegram-bot" target="_blank">python-telegram-bot</a>
            v20+. User kirim <code>/buy 1000</code>, bot bikin invoice, kirim gambar
            QRIS, dan auto-notify pas dibayar.
          </p>
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs mt-2 overflow-x-auto"><code>import asyncio, base64, io, requests
from telegram import Update, InputFile
from telegram.ext import Application, CommandHandler, ContextTypes

PG_BASE    = "<%= baseUrl %>"
PG_API_KEY = "pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"
BOT_TOKEN  = "1234567:AAxxxx"        # dari @BotFather

def create_invoice(amount: int, chat_id: int, order_id: str) -> dict:
    # `merchant_ref` = idempotency key. Kalau bot sudah panggil create_invoice()
    # untuk order_id yang sama & invoice-nya masih PENDING, PG balikin invoice
    # existing (bukan bikin duplikat). Ideal untuk retry setelah network error.
    r = requests.post(
        f"{PG_BASE}/api/v1/invoices",
        headers={"X-API-Key": PG_API_KEY, "Content-Type": "application/json"},
        json={
            "amount":       amount,
            "merchant_ref": f"TG-{chat_id}-{order_id}",
            "description":  f"Order dari Telegram chat {chat_id}",
        },
        timeout=15,
    )
    if r.status_code == 429:
        # Pool unique_code habis. Sleep sesuai Retry-After, lalu retry.
        import time
        time.sleep(int(r.headers.get("Retry-After", "10")))
        return create_invoice(amount, chat_id, order_id)
    r.raise_for_status()
    return r.json()

async def buy(update: Update, ctx: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    if not ctx.args:
        return await update.message.reply_text("Usage: /buy &lt;amount&gt;")
    amount   = int(ctx.args[0])
    chat_id  = update.effective_chat.id
    order_id = str(update.message.message_id)   # unique per message
    inv      = create_invoice(amount, chat_id, order_id)

    # decode qris_image (data:image/png;base64,...) → bytes → kirim sebagai foto
    png = base64.b64decode(inv["qris_image"].split(",", 1)[1])
    caption = (
        f"💰 Bayar sebesar *Rp {inv['total_amount']:,}*\n"
        f"Reference: `{inv['reference']}`\n"
        f"Expired: {inv['expired_at']}"
    )
    await update.message.reply_photo(
        photo=InputFile(io.BytesIO(png), filename="qris.png"),
        caption=caption,
        parse_mode="Markdown",
    )

    # background task: poll status sampai PAID/EXPIRED, kirim notif ke user
    asyncio.create_task(watch_invoice(ctx, chat_id, inv["reference"]))

async def watch_invoice(ctx, chat_id, reference):
    for _ in range(300):                     # max ~15 menit @3s = 300 tries
        await asyncio.sleep(3)
        r = requests.get(
            f"{PG_BASE}/api/v1/invoices/{reference}",
            headers={"X-API-Key": PG_API_KEY},
            timeout=10,
        )
        s = r.json()
        if s["status"] == "PAID":
            await ctx.bot.send_message(chat_id, f"✅ Pembayaran {reference} DITERIMA!")
            return
        if s["status"] in ("EXPIRED", "CANCELLED"):
            await ctx.bot.send_message(chat_id, f"❌ Invoice {reference} {s['status']}")
            return

app = Application.builder().token(BOT_TOKEN).build()
app.add_handler(CommandHandler("buy", buy))
app.run_polling()</code></pre>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">
            Untuk skala lebih besar, ganti polling dengan webhook: server bot
            terima POST di <code>callback_url</code>, verify <code>X-Signature</code>,
            terus kirim notif ke user.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Node.js -->
        <div class="tab-panel hidden" data-tab="node">
<pre class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-3 rounded text-xs mt-3 overflow-x-auto"><code>const axios = require('axios');

const pg = axios.create({
  baseURL: '<%= baseUrl %>/api/v1',
  headers: { 'X-API-Key': 'pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE' },
});

async function main() {
  // 1. Buat invoice
  const { data: inv } = await pg.post('/invoices', {
    amount:       1000,
    merchant_ref: 'ORDER-42',
    description:  'Test dari Node.js',
  });
  console.log('Reference:', inv.reference);
  console.log('Bayar Rp', inv.total_amount);
  console.log('Pay URL :', inv.pay_url);

  // 2. Poll status tiap 3 detik
  while (true) {
    await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 3000));
    const { data: s } = await pg.get(`/invoices/${inv.reference}`);
    console.log('Status:', s.status);
    if (['PAID', 'EXPIRED', 'CANCELLED'].includes(s.status)) break;
  }
}

main().catch(console.error);</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ============ Notes ============ -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded p-3 text-xs text-slate-700">
        <div class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-1">💡 Konsep &amp; batasan yang perlu dipahami</div>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5">
          <li><strong>Bagaimana pembayaran di-match ke invoice?</strong>
            QRIS dari bank / OrderKuota <em>tidak</em> membawa <code>merchant_ref</code>
            kita. Yang muncul di mutasi cuma nominal, keterangan, dan ID
            transaksi dari sisi bank. Jadi satu-satunya cara kita bedain
            invoice adalah <strong>lewat nominal yang unik</strong>. Karena
            itu setiap invoice ditambahi <code>unique_code</code> 1-999
            rupiah — user bayar <code>total_amount</code>, bukan
            <code>amount</code>.</li>
          <li><strong>Idempotency:</strong> kirim <code>merchant_ref</code>
            di setiap POST invoice — retry berapa kali pun aman, tidak
            akan bikin duplikat selama invoice yang lama masih PENDING.
            Kalau kamu tidak kirim <code>merchant_ref</code>, setiap POST
            akan bikin invoice baru.</li>
          <li><strong>Race-safe:</strong> pemilihan <code>unique_code</code> +
            insert Invoice di-serialisasi di dalam satu DB transaction.
            Dua request POST yang masuk bersamaan dengan <code>amount</code>
            sama dijamin tidak akan pernah dapat <code>total_amount</code>
            yang sama.</li>
          <li><strong>Kalau nominal &amp; kode unik sama di dua invoice
            (skenario ekstrem):</strong> selama mekanisme di atas berjalan
            (idempotency + transaction), <em>tidak akan terjadi</em>.
            Andaikan tetap terjadi (bug atau bypass langsung ke DB),
            matcher akan pilih invoice <strong>tertua yang PENDING</strong>
            (FIFO by <code>createdAt</code>). Kita <em>tidak bisa</em> pakai
            <code>merchant_ref</code> untuk disambiguate — field itu tidak
            pernah sampai ke sisi bank / OK.</li>
          <li><strong>Pool <code>unique_code</code> maksimum 999 per
            amount.</strong> Kalau invoice PENDING dengan <code>amount</code>
            sama sudah > 999, POST invoice ke-1000 akan return HTTP 429
            (<code>unique_code_pool_exhausted</code>). Bot: sleep 10 detik
            (lihat header <code>Retry-After</code>) lalu retry, atau
            varietasikan amount (1000, 1001, 1002, ...).</li>
          <li><strong>Poller</strong> jalan setiap ~10 detik untuk cek
            mutasi masuk. Setelah pembayaran diterima OK, invoice paling
            lama 10 detik berubah ke <code>PAID</code>.</li>
          <li><strong>Invoice expire</strong> default 15 menit (ubah lewat
            <code>INVOICE_EXPIRE_MINUTES</code> di <code>.env</code>).
            Semakin cepat expire → pool <code>unique_code</code> berputar
            makin cepat.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    // Tab switcher untuk contoh kode
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const t = btn.dataset.tab;
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach((b) => {
          const active = b.dataset.tab === t;
          b.classList.toggle('border-slate-900', active);
          b.classList.toggle('font-semibold', active);
          b.classList.toggle('border-transparent', !active);
          b.classList.toggle('text-slate-500', !active);
        });
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel').forEach((p) => {
          p.classList.toggle('hidden', p.dataset.tab !== t);
        });
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
